data.description: Barr Homes custom built ranch in popular Shadow Lake 2. Modern ranch style home on the LAST West facing walkout lot on top the hill.  4 bedrooms, 2 up and 2 down.  Open floor plan with finished walkout basement with daylight windows. Kitchen with custom cabinets, vented cooktop hood, huge dinette, center island & walk-in pantry. Great Room with recessed ceiling detail, stone fireplace, accent wall, cabinets & large windows for daylight. Large drop zone between garage and kitchen. Primary bedroom with recessed ceiling and large walk-in closet. Primary bath has extra large double sink vanity and huge walk-in tiled shower. Covered front porch with grand stone entry columns. Large 3 car garage with extra extended bay is great for storage! Finished basement with a wet bar great for entertaining. AMA. Pictures may be of similar completed home.
